==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: mǎzǐ
===[[Min Nan]]===
[[POJ]]: bé-chí

===Etymology===
According to legend, a [[w:Han Dynasty|Han Dynasty]] emperor had a commode in the shape of a tiger, termed [[虎子]].  A later [[w:Tang Dynasty|Tang Dynasty]] emperor had the commode renamed [[兽子]] or '''马子''', because one of his ancestors had the character [[虎]] as a given name.  During the [[w:Song Dynasty|Song Dynasty]], the term was changed to [[马桶]].[http://72.14.203.104/search?q=cache:I7KjOXi7LiUJ:iask.jiaju.sina.com.cn/b/501603.html%3Ffrom%3Drelated+%E6%9D%8E%E8%99%8E+%22%E9%A6%AC%E6%A1%B6%22+site:.cn&hl=zh-TW&gl=tw&ct=clnk&cd=16]

===Noun===
'''[[马]][[子]]'''

# gambling chip
# [[commode]], [[nightstool]], a seat over a [[chamberpot]]
